`,` Sort files
`f` Filter files

## Navigation

Key | Action
-----------|-----------------
`k` / `↑` | Move cursor up |
`j` / `↓` | Move cursor down |
`l` / `→` | Enter hovered directory |
`h` / `←` | Leave current directory (go to parent) |
`K` | Seek up 5 units in preview |
`J` | Seek down 5 units in preview |
`g` `g` | Move cursor to top |
`G` | Move cursor to bottom |
`z` | Change directory via zoxide |

## Selection

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `Space` | Toggle selection of hovered file/directory |
| `v` | Enter visual mode (selection mode) |
| `V` | Enter visual mode (unset mode) |
| `Ctrl + a` | Select all files |
| `Ctrl + r` | Inverse selection |
| `Esc` | Cancel selection |

## File Operations

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `o` | Open selected files |
| `O` | Open selected files interactively |
| `Enter` | Open selected files |
| `Shift + Enter` | Open selected files interactively |
| `Tab` | Show file information |
| `y` | Yank (copy) selected files |
| `x` | Yank (cut) selected files |
| `p` | Paste yanked files |
| `P` | Paste yanked files (overwrite) |
| `Y` / `X` | Cancel yank status |
| `d` | Trash selected files |
| `D` | Permanently delete selected files |
| `a` | Create file (end with `/` for directories) |
| `r` | Rename selected file(s) |
| `.` | Toggle hidden files visibility |

## Shell Commands

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `;` | Run shell command |
| `:` | Run shell command (block until finishes) |

## Links

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `-` | Symlink absolute path of yanked files |
| `_` | Symlink relative path of yanked files |
| `Ctrl + -` | Hardlink yanked files |

## Copy Paths

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `c` `c` | Copy file path |
| `c` `d` | Copy directory path |
| `c` `f` | Copy filename |
| `c` `n` | Copy filename without extension |

## Filter & Find

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `f` | Filter files |
| `/` | Find next file |
| `?` | Find previous file |
| `n` | Go to next found |
| `N` | Go to previous found |

## Search

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `s` | Search files by name using ripgrep |

## Sorting

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `,` `m` | Sort by modified time |
| `,` `M` | Sort by modified time (reverse) |
| `,` `b` | Sort by birth time |
| `,` `B` | Sort by birth time (reverse) |
| `,` `e` | Sort by file extension |
| `,` `E` | Sort by file extension (reverse) |
| `,` `a` | Sort alphabetically |
| `,` `A` | Sort alphabetically (reverse) |
| `,` `n` | Sort naturally |
| `,` `N` | Sort naturally (reverse) |
| `,` `s` | Sort by size |
| `,` `S` | Sort by size (reverse) |
| `,` `r` | Sort randomly |

## Multi-tab

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `t` | Create new tab with current directory |
| `1`-`9` | Switch to N-th tab |
| `[` | Switch to previous tab |
| `]` | Switch to next tab |
| `{` | Swap current tab with previous |
| `}` | Swap current tab with next |
| `Ctrl + c` | Close current tab |
